{
  "stem": "21139.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was-- they had a piece of string.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was measured.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The bread, the loaf of bread was measured.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was then each one got one slice of bread in 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] if God forbid somebody got a little bit more, it was unbelievable how people-- how angry people became.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We got-- they gave us some hot soup.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was no soup.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was just water with something floating in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some-- sometimes it was some tomatoes or something like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is-- and black coffee we got in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's what we lived on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There-- the hygienic-- the facilities were unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, we had-- on the outside, it was cold-- some cold water running certain times, so we washed ourselves as good as we could.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The bathrooms were-- there were no bathrooms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was just holes outside somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and it was cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was November already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was near-- it was the Pyrenees.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was cold and it was raining.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we had-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we washed ourselves as good as we could.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And of course, after a while, we had-- we were-- had lice from top to bottom.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And once one of those Gypsies came and had like a bottle of some kind of a medication for against lice.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "My mother gave her piece of bread away in order to get that so she and I could be clean too.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we washed ourselves outside in cold water in the cold as good as we could.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "This-- and this is how we lived until they took us to a different camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was packed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were not in cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
